dialogAfv.label: Please let us know whether you would like to Renew, Retain or Return your vehicle.
If you would like to upgrade your vehicle to a new model and trade in your current model, please request Renew.
If you would like to keep your vehicle, please request Retain.  You can request to either finance the final Future Value payment or pay the Future Value in full.
If you would like to return the vehicle, please request Return and we will remind you of the return criteria, fees and process.
Some requests may be subject to lending criteria.
